  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this <strong>S</strong>elf <strong>I</strong>nflicted <strong>P</strong>uzzle <strong>E</strong>xperience your goal is to assemble all puzzle pieces in several jigsaws. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 50+ puzzles are waiting to be solved. But you are also able to turn all your beloved pictures into you very own jigsaw. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For all jigsaw lovers this game provides various tools to even manage puzzles with 5.000 pieces (or more if you dare). Different sorting and arrangement tools support you, so you only do what is the most fun: find where this strange piece have to go!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this <strong>S</strong>elf <strong>I</strong>nflicted <strong>P</strong>uzzle <strong>E</strong>xperience your goal is to assemble all puzzle pieces in several jigsaws. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 50+ puzzles are waiting to be solved. But you are also able to turn all your beloved pictures into you very own jigsaw. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For all jigsaw lovers this game provides various tools to even manage puzzles with 5.000 pieces (or more if you dare). Different sorting and arrangement tools support you, so you only do what is the most fun: find where this strange piece have to go!</p>",
